OL,3,CHouseholds set for lower energy bills
OL,4,Camid price cap shake-up
OL,6,FHouseholds' energy bills will fall by
OL,7,Faround 7% from April in a shake-up of
OL,8,Fcosts after the government promised
OL,9,Fthey will receive an average #150 cut.
OL,11,FLatest predictions suggest Ofgem will
OL,12,Freduce the energy price cap by #117 to
OL,13,F#1,641 a year for a typical dual fuel
OL,14,Fhousehold from April 1, when it makes
OL,15,Fits announcement on Wednesday.
