OL,3,CHouseholds set for lower energy bills
OL,4,Camid price cap shake-up
OL,6,FThe reduction is expected to be
OL,7,Fprimarily applied through a lower
OL,8,Fprice per unit of electricity used,
OL,9,Fwith households advised to look out
OL,10,Ffor information from their supplier
OL,11,Fexplaining this after the price cap
OL,12,Fannouncement.
OL,14,FCornwall Insight said the changes will
OL,15,Freduce the cap by about #145 a year
OL,16,Fonce VAT and pricing allowances within
OL,17,Fthe cap methodology are taken into
OL,18,Faccount.
