OL,6,FIt added that increases in charges
OL,7,Fassociated with the operation and
OL,8,Fmaintenance of Britain's energy
OL,9,Fnetworks have offset part of the
OL,10,Fsavings.
OL,12,FWholesale prices had also risen
OL,13,Fslightly since its last forecast in
OL,14,FDecember, with the cost of gas
OL,15,Fparticularly volatile due to
OL,16,F"geopolitical factors".
