OL,6,FLooking further ahead, Cornwall said
OL,7,Fwholesale costs were still lower than
OL,8,Fwhen Ofgem set the January cap level
OL,9,Fand it expected the cap to remain
OL,10,F"relatively steady" throughout 2026,
OL,11,F"with only a small rise forecast in
OL,12,FJuly".
